---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-[#1C1814] text-white mt-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-8 py-14">
    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-[#B5634B] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-black text-lg">Hayvan Hakları Platformu</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#8A7B6F] leading-relaxed max-w-sm text-sm">
          Sessiz bırakılan canların sesi. Hayvan hakları ihlallerini görünür kılmak,
          toplumsal farkındalık oluşturmak için bağımsız bir platform.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-6">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/hayvanhaklariplatformuturkiye/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-white/10 hover:bg-[#B5634B] flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://x.com/HayvanHTP" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-white/10 hover:bg-[#B5634B] flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@HAYVANHAKLARIT%C3%9CRK%C4%B0YEPLATFORMU/featured" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-white/10 hover:bg-[#B5634B] flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22.54 6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.95-1.96C18.88 4 12 4 12 4s-6.88 0-8.59.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.95 1.96A29 29 0 0 0 1 12a29 29 0 0 0 .46 5.58A2.78 2.78 0 0 0 3.41 19.6C5.12 20 12 20 12 20s6.88 0 8.59-.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.95-1.95A29 29 0 0 0 23 12a29 29 0 0 0-.46-5.58z"/><polygon points="9.75 15.02 15.5 12 9.75 8.98 9.75 15.02"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-[#8A7B6F] mb-4">Sayfalar</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {[
            { href: "/",           label: "Ana Sayfa" },
            { href: "/manifesto",  label: "Manifesto" },
            { href: "/haberler",   label: "Haberler" },
            { href: "/hakkimizda", label: "Hakkımızda" },
          ].map(l => (
            <li><a href={l.href} class="text-[#8A7B6F] hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors">{l.label}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-[#8A7B6F] mb-4">İletişim</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#8A7B6F]">
          <li>
            <a href="mailto:hayvanhaklariplatformuturkiye@gmail.com"
               class="hover:text-white transition-colors break-all leading-relaxed">
              hayvanhaklariplatformuturkiye@gmail.com
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-white/10">
            <a href="/iletisim" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[#B5634B] hover:text-[#D4856E] font-semibold transition-colors">
              Bize ulaşın →
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs text-[#6B5E55]">
      <p>© {year} Hayvan Hakları Türkiye Platformu. Tüm hakları saklıdır.</p>
      <p>Yaşam hakkı pazarlık konusu değildir.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
